{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_a2d3b428-5d5f-46f1-be66-74dd5c9e22c","tool_call":{"mcpToolCall":{"args":{"name":"firecrawl-firecrawl_scrape","args":{"url":"https://forbsab.se/en","formats":["markdown"],"onlyMainContent":true},"toolCallId":"tool_a2d3b428-5d5f-46f1-be66-74dd5c9e22c","providerIdentifier":"firecrawl","toolName":"firecrawl_scrape"},"result":{"success":{"content":[{"text":{"text":"{\n  \"markdown\": \"![White Forbs logo](https://forbsab.se/_astro/logo-white.cd169f23.svg)\\n\\n# Building the future   here and now\\n\\nContact us\\n\\n![Mobile menu icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/hamburger-menu.b027c3a9.svg)[SV](https://forbsab.se/sv)\\n\\n## Building trust\\n\\n### Flexible\\n\\n![Trust Flexible icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/trust__flexible.1ae094dd.svg)\\n\\nWe are highly adaptable to the unique challenges and changes each project presents.\\n\\n### Organized\\n\\n![Trust Organized icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/trust__organized.5e87e21c.png)\\n\\nThanks to our broad in-house expertise, we're equipped to tackle any unforeseen challenge.\\n\\n### Respectful\\n\\n![Trust Respectful icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/trust__respectful.55fa2f33.png)\\n\\nWe treat our customers with respect, dignity, and professionalism — as a matter of principle.\\n\\n### Breaking Ground\\n\\n![Trust Breaking Ground icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/trust__pioneering.441c00ea.png)\\n\\nWe actively contribute to our clients’ success by delivering solutions that simplify both project execution and administrative workflows.\\n\\n### Service-oriented\\n\\n![Trust Service-oriented icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/trust__service-oriented.64805ebf.png)\\n\\nWe are responsive to the customer's wishes and ensure a high standard of communication. Quality and customer satisfaction are always in focus for us.\\n\\n![Trust background image](https://forbsab.se/_astro/logo.839da44e.svg)\\n\\n## Building trust\\n\\nFor us, staying at the forefront of technology and embracing the most innovative solutions in materials, sustainability, and construction is a fundamental part of our mission.\\n\\n![Technologies image 2](https://forbsab.se/_astro/2.9def8bd4.jpg)\\n\\n### Brief facts\\n\\n- High credit rating\\n- Well-trained and certified staff\\n- Authorization for wet room work\\n- Member of Byggföretagen\\n\\n## Construction services suitable for homes and industries\\n\\nWith our extensive experience and broad expertise, we handle everything from the most complex construction projects to simpler assignments. As a reliable organization, we support our employees to ensure the highest quality in every project.\\n\\n\\n### Our management works daily with\\n\\n- Customer focus\\n- Strategic leadership\\n- Committed and motivated employees\\n- Process optimization\\n- Continuous development\\n- Digitalization\\n- Relationship and network management\\n\\nHire us\\n\\n### Project planning\\n\\n![Services Project planning icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/services__project-planning.fe78cfbe.png)\\n\\n### Construction services\\n\\n![Services Construction services icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/services__construction-services.9ac4c667.png)\\n\\n### Staffing\\n\\n![Services Staffing icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/services__staffing.527229aa.png)\\n\\n### Plumbing Services\\n\\n![Services Plumbing Services icon](https://forbsab.se/_astro/services__vvs.04b1c120.png)\\n\\n![Our services background image](https://forbsab.se/_astro/logo.839da44e.svg)\\n\\n## About us\\n\\n![About us image 2](https://forbsab.se/_astro/2.7ba16e3f.jpg)\\n\\n![About us image 3](https://forbsab.se/_astro/3.f3499131.jpg)\\n\\n50+\\nEmployees\\n\\n## About us\\n\\n**Forbs AB** is a company in the construction industry, headquartered in Stockholm, with around 50 employees.\\n\\nThe company was founded in 2017.\\n\\nWe carry out carpentry, concrete work, painting, tiling, and staffing services. We also offer consulting services in architecture and construction, as well as site management and project coordination.\\n\\nWe always put the customer first, and every project is carried out with great responsibility. When you hire Forbs AB, you can be confident that the work will be completed to the highest standards and delivered on time.\\n\\nOur goal is to consistently deliver high-quality results that exceed our customers’ expectations. We work in accordance with current building standards and ensure that all projects are completed within the agreed time and budget, in close cooperation with our clients.\\n\\n## Contact\\n\\n![contact.attributes[\\\"Name\\\"] photo](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Jan_1d12490603.jpg)\\n\\n### Jan Kotkas\\n\\nVD, Kalkyl, Projektledningjan@forbsab.se08 82 6368\\n\\n![contact.attributes[\\\"Name\\\"] photo](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Dima_7a04e19984.jpg)\\n\\n### Dmitry Nesterenko\\n\\nFörsäljning, projektledningdima@forbsab.se+46 73 569 40 18\\n\\n![contact.attributes[\\\"Name\\\"] photo](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Yura_a19eacad41.jpg)\\n\\n### Yurii Naumov\\n\\nIngenjöryurii@forbsab.se+46 73 923 78 46\\n\\n![contact.attributes[\\\"Name\\\"] photo](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Aleksei_7f673702b7.jpg)\\n\\n### Aleksei Marinin\\n\\nProjektledare aleksei@forbsab.se+46 76 590 68 69\\n\\n![contact.attributes[\\\"Name\\\"] photo](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Artjom_4b3b213dab.jpg)\\n\\n### Artjom Novoksonov\\n\\nArbetsledareartjom@forbsab.se+46 76 905 01 42\\n\\n![contact.attributes[\\\"Name\\\"] photo](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Violla_9559e6dd25.jpg)\\n\\n### Violla Kotkas\\n\\nMediaviolla@forbsab.se\\n\\n![contact.attributes[\\\"Name\\\"] photo](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Elina_69bc2a44ff.jpg)\\n\\n### Elina Nilsson\\n\\nAdministration, ekonomielina@forbsab.se+46 70 026 52 62\\n\\n## Quality policy\\n\\n- We strive to build long-term, sustainable relationships with our customers by always acting with integrity and strong business ethics.\\n- Each employee possesses the necessary competence, takes responsibility, and demonstrates strong commitment to their tasks.\\n- Each project is carefully planned in advance to ensure quality and avoid defects.\\n- We continuously develop our expertise by staying up to date on market trends, new products, suppliers, and changes in legislation and environmental regulations. We also invest in ongoing training for our staH. By continuously improving our operations and management systems, we ensure the highest possible results.\\n\\n![Quality policy image](https://forbsab.se/_astro/quality-policy.fc17a552.jpg)\\n\\n![Quality policy image](https://forbsab.se/_astro/environment-policy.45c0c448.png)Forbs AB is committed to fostering a work environment that promotes health and prevents illness for both employees and partners. Through our active involvement in every project, we work systematically to minimize our environmental impact. Our goal is to continuously improve our methods to ensure the highest standards of safety and quality, while delivering sustainable outcomes that contribute to environmental and social progress.\\n\\n## Environment policy\\n\\n- We take responsibility for the environment by complying with all relevant laws and regulations, and by actively working to minimize our environmental impact.\\n- We are committed to reducing energy and material consumption across all our projects.\\n- We continuously improve our processes and encourage employees to support sustainable development by finding innovative, sustainable solutions.\\n- We work closely with our clients to ensure optimal material and transport planning—both cost-effective and environmentally sound.\\n- We strive to design and build energy-efficient buildings.\\n- We inform, train, and engage our staff on environmental issues.\\n- We practice waste separation and recycling at all worksites to maximize material reuse and reduce overall waste.\\n- Our vehicles and equipment always meet the latest environmental standards, and we work systematically to reduce emissions and other environmental impacts.\\n\\n## Latest news\\n\\n![VVS-Avdelning image](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Skaermavbild_2025_07_20_kl_17_43_55_2de5a898c2.png)\\n\\n### VVS-Avdelning\\n\\nVi har nöjet att informera om att vi nu har etablerat en VVS-avdelning inom vår verksamhet. Genom denna satsning kan vi erbjuda våra kunder ett ännu bredare utbud av tjänster, med fokus på hög kvalitet, service och professionalism. Vårt erfarna team står till ert förfogande för installation, service och rådgivning.\\nVälkommen att kontakta oss för mer information.\\n\\n![Projekt i fokus – Tyresö image](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Skaermavbild_2025_05_08_kl_22_44_18_1c29858c6d.png)\\n\\n### Projekt i fokus – Tyresö\\n\\nVi på Forbs Bygg är stolta över att ha varit delaktiga i ännu ett framgångsrikt projekt – denna gång i Tyresö på uppdrag av Hawila. Projektet omfattade stomkompletteringsarbeten i tre huskroppar: Hus A, B och C, där en särskilt viktig del har varit monteringen av fallskyddssystem på taken enligt alla gällande säkerhetskrav. Säkerheten är och förblir vår högsta prioritet på alla våra byggarbetsplatser, och att skapa en trygg miljö för både medarbetare och samarbetspartners är en självklarhet. Vi tackar Hawila för förtroendet och ser fram emot fler spännande samarbeten framöver!\\n\\n![Stomkomplettering och Fasadmontage image](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Skaermavbild_2025_06_27_kl_14_55_39_25f7c0f939.png)\\n\\n### Stomkomplettering och Fasadmontage\\n\\nStomkompletteringen på ett av våra större projekt från 2024 pågår för fullt, med fokus på montage av ventilerad träfasad. Arbetet utförs med hög precision av våra medarbetare och visar hur gediget hantverk förverkligar arkitektoniska visioner. Ett viktigt projekt som stärker vår portfölj inom avancerade byggnationer i Stockholm.\\n\\n![Projekt i fokus – Wästbygg image](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Skaermavbild_2025_07_20_kl_17_39_02_4ea6146051.png)\\n\\n### Projekt i fokus – Wästbygg\\n\\nStort tack till Wästbygg för ett fint samarbete i bostadsprojektet i Bromma. Forbs har bidragit med rumsbildning, montagearbeten, golv och våtrum – allt utfört med kvalitet och god samordning. Vi ser fram emot fler samarbeten!\\n\\n![Projekt i fokus - Uppsala image](https://forbs-ab-admin.fly.dev/uploads/Skaermavbild_2025_05_08_kl_22_36_27_d466cd87b4.png)\\n\\n### Projekt i fokus - Uppsala\\n\\nI Uppsala pågår just nu ett nytt bostadsprojekt där Forbs byggavdelning ansvarar för stomkomplettering och montage av takkonstruktionen, helt enligt projektets tidplan. Arbetet omfattar flera moment som ställer höga krav på precision, effektiv logistik och yrkesskicklighet – något vi levererar med fullt fokus genom hela processen.\\n\\n## Our partners\",\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"language\": \"en\",\n    \"viewport\": \"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\",\n    \"og:title\": \"Forbs AB - We build the future here and now\",\n    \"robots\": \"index, follow\",\n    \"description\": \"With long experience and broad competence, we undertake everything from complicated to simpler construction projects. We have a strong organization that stands behind our employees regarding execution.\",\n    \"theme-color\": \"#ffffff\",\n    \"title\": \"Forbs AB - We build the future here and now\",\n    \"og:description\": \"With long experience and broad competence, we undertake everything from complicated to simpler construction projects. We have a strong organization that stands behind our employees regarding execution.\",\n    \"msapplication-TileColor\": \"#da532c\",\n    \"favicon\": \"https://forbsab.se/favicon-32x32.png\",\n    \"scrapeId\": \"019be3e3-58ed-71eb-ae00-a22e237225b1\",\n    \"sourceURL\": \"https://forbsab.se/en\",\n    \"url\": \"https://forbsab.se/en\",\n    \"statusCode\": 200,\n    \"contentType\": \"text/html\",\n    \"timezone\": \"America/New_York\",\n    \"proxyUsed\": \"basic\",\n    \"cacheState\": \"miss\",\n    \"indexId\": \"28cd57c6-2e47-46cd-9cc4-ac1a19d68439\",\n    \"creditsUsed\": 1,\n    \"concurrencyLimited\": false\n  }\n}"}}],"isError":false}}}},"model_call_id":"1605d83d-fcd7-46bb-bbdf-36cee5f85822-6-ymey","session_id":"6114be38-83fc-48b6-856a-2e3ca66f416b","timestamp_ms":1769054889655}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_c5f47d40-2973-4e22-b5a3-fefca3d6539","tool_call":{"mcpToolCall":{"args":{"name":"firecrawl-firecrawl_scrape","args":{"url":"https://www.frankskyttberg.se/kontakt","formats":["markdown"],"onlyMainContent":true},"toolCallId":"tool_c5f47d40-2973-4e22-b5a3-fefca3d6539","providerIdentifier":"firecrawl","toolName":"firecrawl_scrape"},"result":{"success":{"content":[{"text":{"text":"{\n  \"markdown\": \"[![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/assets/images/lang-sv.png)](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/kontakt)[![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/assets/images/lang-uk.png)](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/kontakt)\\n\\n# Kontakt\\n\\n## Skicka ett meddelande till oss idag\\n\\nSkicka ett meddelande till oss idag med hjälp av formuläret eller kontakta oss via informationen nedan. Vi hjälper dig gärna med dina frågor. Vi kommer att svara så snart som möjligt.\\n\\n##### Frank & Skyttberg Construction Company AB\\n\\n- [Albybergsringen 105, 137 69 Österhaninge](https://maps.app.goo.gl/gJa74QWsGvqmQTQ58)\\n- [070-632 32 33](tel:070-632 32 33)\\n- [info@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:info@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n###### Faktureringsuppgifter:\\n\\n##### Frank & Skyttberg Construction Company AB\\n\\nFE 20675\\n\\n838 76 Frösön\\n\\nEller maila din faktura till [faktura@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:Faktura@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\nAlla fakturor ska vara märkta med ett p nummer (PXXXX)\\n\\n[Läs mer här](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/brevanginscanning.pdf)\\n\\nJag ger mitt medgivande till att denna hemsida sparar informationen i detta formulär i syfte att kunna kontakta mig.\\n\\nSkriv följande siffror i fältet (43929)\\n\\nSkicka meddelande\\n\\n## Möt laget\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/fredrik-frank-.jpg)\\n\\n##### Fredrik Frank\\n\\n###### Projektledare mark.\\n\\n[070 632 32 33](tel:070%20632%2032%2033)\\n\\n[fredrik@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:fredrik@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/andreas.jpg)\\n\\n##### Andreas Skyttberg\\n\\n###### Kvalitets och miljöansvarig / Ekonomi\\n\\n[070 384 30 20](tel:070%20384%2030%2020)\\n\\n[andreas@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:andreas@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/kamilla-zielinska.jpg)\\n\\n##### Kamilla Zielinska\\n\\n###### Admin / Ekonomi\\n\\n[kamilla.Zielinska@talenom.se](mailto:kamilla.Zielinska@talenom.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/anders-gylfe.jpg)\\n\\n##### Anders Gylfe\\n\\n###### Projektledare Bygg\\n\\n[070 632 32 85](tel:070%20632%2032%2085) [anders@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:anders@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/tommie-danielsson.jpg)\\n\\n##### Tommie Danielsson\\n\\n###### Arbetsledare\\n\\n[070 632 32 58](tel:070%20632%2032%2058)\\n\\n[tommie@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:tommie@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/kjell-frisk.jpg)\\n\\n##### Kjell Frisk\\n\\n###### Jourledare / Vinterunderhåll\\n\\n[070 632 32 67](tel:070%20632%2032%2067)\\n\\n[kjell@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:kjell@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/pajtim-hed.jpg)\\n\\n##### Pajtim Hed\\n\\n###### Platsansvarig\\n\\n[070 632 32 74](tel:070%20632%2032%2074)\\n\\n[pajtim@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:pajtim@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/william-moebyus.jpg)\\n\\n##### William Moebius\\n\\n###### Platsansvarig\\n\\n[william@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:william@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/hkan-hallgren.jpg)\\n\\n##### Håkan Hallgren\\n\\n###### Platsansvarig\\n\\n[073 056 44 51](tel:073%20056%2044%2051)\\n\\n[hakan@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:hakan@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/mikael-pettersson.jpg)\\n\\n##### Mikael Pettersson\\n\\n###### Platsansvarig\\n\\n[mikael@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:mikael@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/serghii-benediuk.jpg)\\n\\n##### Serghii Benediuk\\n\\n###### Platsansvarig\\n\\n[serghii@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:serghii@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/mikael-hallin.jpg)\\n\\n##### Mikael Hallin\\n\\n###### Skötsel och eftervård trädgård\\n\\n[076 090 25 57](tel:076%20090%2025%2057)\\n\\n[mikael.h@frankskyttberg.se](mailto:mikael.h@frankskyttberg.se)\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/martin-plzak.jpg)\\n\\n##### Martin Plzak\\n\\n###### Anläggare\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/ivan-sobel.jpg)\\n\\n##### Ivan Sobel\\n\\n###### Anläggare\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/erik-larsson.jpg)\\n\\n##### Erik Larsson\\n\\n###### Anläggare\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/johnny-stenman.jpg)\\n\\n##### Johnny Stenman\\n\\n###### Lastbil\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/daniel-ossowski.jpg)\\n\\n##### Daniel Ossowski\\n\\n###### Snickare\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/wincent-lord.jpg)\\n\\n##### Wincent Lord\\n\\n###### Anläggare\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/leo-skyttberg.jpg)\\n\\n##### Leo Skyttberg\\n\\n###### Säkerhetsansvarig\\n\\n![](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/files/staff/nils-frank.jpg)\\n\\n##### Nils Frank\\n\\n###### Framtiden\\n\\nBESbswy\\n\\n[Hem](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/)\\n[Om oss](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/om-oss)\\n[Tjänster](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/tjanster)\\n- [Mark & Anläggning](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/tjanster/mark--anlaggning)\\n- [Dränering](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/tjanster/dranering)\\n- [Snöröjning](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/tjanster/snorojning)\\n- [Bygg](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/tjanster/bygg)\\n- [Liggande stammar](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/tjanster/liggande-stammar)\\n- [Parkering/Laddplats](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/tjanster/parkeringladdplats)\\n[Referenser](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/referenser)\\n- [Torget](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/referenser/torget)\\n- [Anpassning i BRF lokal](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/referenser/anpassning-i-brf-lokal)\\n- [Lekplatsrenovering](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/referenser/lekplatsrenovering)\\n- [Dränering/grundisoleringsarbete (En BRF)](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/referenser/draneringgrundisoleringsarbete-en-brf)\\n[Samarbetspartner](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/samarbetspartner)\\n[Jobba hos oss](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/jobba-hos-oss)\\n[Kontakt](https://www.frankskyttberg.se/kontakt)\",\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"og:description\": \"Ett heltäckande mark- och anläggningsföretag som har den kunskap och erfarenhet som krävs för att erbjuda allt från spade till grävmaskin - helt i egen regi.\",\n    \"ogTitle\": \"Frank & Skyttberg Construction Company AB\",\n    \"ogUrl\": \"https://www.frankskyttberg.se/\",\n    \"og:url\": \"https://www.frankskyttberg.se/\",\n    \"og:title\": \"Frank & Skyttberg Construction Company AB\",\n    \"og:image\": \"https://www.frankskyttberg.se/assets/images/site_preview.jpg\",\n    \"title\": \"Frank & Skyttberg Construction Company AB\",\n    \"ogDescription\": \"Ett heltäckande mark- och anläggningsföretag som har den kunskap och erfarenhet som krävs för att erbjuda allt från spade till grävmaskin - helt i egen regi.\",\n    \"ogImage\": \"https://www.frankskyttberg.se/assets/images/site_preview.jpg\",\n    \"keywords\": \"mark, anläggning, spade, grävmaskin, dränering, handen, grundisolering, avloppsanläggningar, gårdsrenovering, stenläggning\",\n    \"language\": \"sv\",\n    \"og:type\": \"\",\n    \"robots\": \"index\",\n    \"description\": \"Ett heltäckande mark- och anläggningsföretag som har den kunskap och erfarenhet som krävs för att erbjuda allt från spade till grävmaskin - helt i egen regi.\",\n    \"viewport\": \"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no\",\n    \"favicon\": \"https://www.frankskyttberg.se/assets/images/favicon.png\",\n    \"scrapeId\"